item.description: BenYourKing is a graduate student in the school of journalism and communication of NanJing University. He’s major is computational social science. He has a strong interest in ML and NLP. He has a solid experience in the network and new media industry for more than 5 years. Throughout his career, he has built a number of large-scale, cross-country OSS/BSS platforms/systems and operation tools, most of them are still running in productions.
